<item>
            <title>[SPARK-14074] Use fixed version of install_github in SparkR build</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-14074</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In dev/lint-r.R, `install_github` makes our builds depend on a unstable source. We should use official releases on CRAN instead even the released version has less feature.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;cc: &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=shivaram&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;shivaram&quot;&gt;shivaram&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=sunrui&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;sunrui&quot;&gt;sunrui&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
